20Hate%20Speech%2C%20Stoking%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F25115737%2F22.2.22-58.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20issued%20directives%20to%20district%20magistrates%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Yavatmal%20and%20Chhattisgrah%E2%80%99s%20Raipur%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-hate-speech-bjp-mla-t-raja-singh-hindu-janajagruti-samiti-246897%5C%22%3Etake%20appropriate%20measures%20in%20response%20to%20concerns%20about%20potential%20hate%20speeches%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20upcoming%20rallies%20organised%20by%20the%20Hindu%20Janajagruti%20Samiti%20(HJS)%20and%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20legislator%20T.%20Raja%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHJS%20plans%20to%20conduct%20rallies%20in%20Yavatmal%20on%20January%2018%20and%20in%20Raipur%20from%20January%2019%20to%20January%2025.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20court%20declined%20to%20halt%20the%20rallies%2C%20it%20instructed%20the%20district%20magistrates%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20hate%20speech%20occurs%20during%20these%20events.%20The%20court%20also%20suggested%20the%20installation%20of%20CCTV%20cameras%20at%20the%20locations%20to%20identify%20perpetrators%20in%20case%20of%20any%20%E2%80%9Cuntoward%20incidents%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-hate-speech-bjp-mla-t-raja-singh-hindu-janajagruti-samiti-246897%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decision%20came%20during%20the%20hearing%20of%20an%20interlocutory%20application%20seeking%20to%20deny%20permission%20for%20the%20rallies.%20The%20application%20included%20transcripts%20of%20alleged%20hate%20speeches%20made%20by%20the%20organisations%20and%20Singh%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20representing%20applicant%20Shaheen%20Abdullah%2C%20expressed%20dissatisfaction%20with%20the%20lack%20of%20action%20against%20Singh%20despite%20previous%20FIRs.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20event%20takes%20place%2C%20we%20come%20to%20this%20court%20and%20an%20FIR%20is%20lodged.%20But%20nothing%20is%20done.%20Then%20he%20continues%20with%20this%20kind%20of%20speeches.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20all%20this%20then%3F%20See%20the%20kind%20of%20hatred%20he%20is%20propagating!%E2%80%9D%20Sibal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-hate-speech-bjp-mla-t-raja-singh-hindu-janajagruti-samiti-246897%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Justice%20Khanna%20acknowledged%20the%20objectionable%20nature%20of%20the%20speeches%2C%20he%20stressed%20upon%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20intervene%20once%20the%20criminal%20justice%20process%20is%20set%20in%20motion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20through%20%5Bthe%20speeches%5D.%20Certainly%20objectionable.%20%5BBut%5D%20this%20court%20has%20already%20issued%20directions%2C%20including%20regarding%20CCTV%20cameras.%20As%20far%20as%20processions%20are%20concerned%E2%80%A6we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20stop%20that.%20If%20there%E2%80%99s%20any%20hate%20speech%20or%20incitement%20to%20violence%2C%20we%20will%20take%20action.%20But%20we%20cannot%20preempt%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-hate-speech-bjp-mla-t-raja-singh-hindu-janajagruti-samiti-246897%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Datta%20pointed%20to%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%20and%20said%20that%20the%20alleged%20perpetrators%20should%20be%20parties%20in%20the%20case.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIs%20he%20a%20party%3F%20Your%20request%2C%20if%20granted%2C%20will%20affect%20someone.%20Your%20prayer%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20permission%20is%20not%20granted%20to%20X%20or%20withdraw%20permission%20if%20already%20granted%3F%20How%20can%20we%20pass%20this%20order%20without%20this%20person%20being%20a%20party%20or%20hearing%20them%3F%20This%20goes%20against%20the%20fundamental%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-hate-speech-bjp-mla-t-raja-singh-hindu-janajagruti-samiti-246897%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20happen%20again%20and%20again%20unless%20your%20lordships%20intervene%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sibal%20said%20at%20the%20end.%20However%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20passed%20orders.%20In%20one%20case%2C%20we%20had%20passed%20orders%20and%20it%20did%20stop.%20That%20is%20the%20positive%20part.%20Why%20only%20look%20at%20the%20negative%20aspect%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20was%20booked%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20Police%20on%20January%207%20for%20allegedly%20making%20incendiary%20speeches%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Solapur%20on%20January%206.%20During%20the%20rally%2C%20he%20allegedly%20urged%20his%20audience%20to%20assault%20%E2%80%9Clove%20jihadis%E2%80%9D%20and%20boycott%20products%20with%20halal%20certification%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENews%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftelangana%2Ftelangana-bjp-mla-raja-singh-booked-for-hate-speech-in-maharashtras-solapur-rally%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20term%20Hindutva%20politicians%20have%20coined%20and%20used%20to%20describe%20an%20imaginary%20conspiracy%20in%20which%20Muslim%20men%20supposedly%20dupe%20unsuspecting%20Hindu%20women%20into%20marriage%20in%20order%20to%20convert%20them%20to%20Islam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20called%20for%20demolition%20of%20mosques%20in%20contested%20sites%20claimed%20to%20have%20formerly%20housed%20Hindu%20places%20of%20worship%2C%20and%20suggested%20that%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20provide%20bulldozers%20to%20MLAs%20and%20MPs%20to%20be%20used%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20does%2C%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20also%20was%20suspended%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20August%20last%20year%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bjp-suspension-t-raja-singh-comments-prophet-muhammad%5C%22%3Ehis%20comments%20caused%20communal%20tensions%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705561478000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F25115737%2F22.2.22-58.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsc-refuses-to-cancel-rally-of-bjp-leader-infamous-for-hate-speech-stoking-violence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20court%20declined%20to%20halt%20the%20rallies%2C%20it%20suggested%20the%20installation%20of%20CCTV%20cameras%20at%20the%20locations%20to%20identify%20perpetrators%20in%20case%20of%20any%20%E2%80%9Cuntoward%20incidents%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsc-refuses-to-cancel-rally-of-bjp-leader-infamous-for-hate-speech-stoking-violence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20launches%20retaliatory%20strikes%20on%20Iran%2C%20with%20reports%20of%20seven%20killed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705561471000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0AC3%2Fproduction%2F_132355720_bordercheck.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68014882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seven%20people%20are%20reported%20to%20have%20been%20kille