tize%20flight%20safety%20once%20she%20takes%20over%20as%20president%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmainichi.jp%2Fenglish%2Farticles%2F20240117%2Fp2g%2F00m%2F0bu%2F048000c%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSpeaking%2520at%2520a%2520press%2520conference%2Cis%2520the%2520foundation%2520of%2520airlines.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20newspaper%20The%20Mainichi.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSafety%20is%20the%20foundation%20of%20airlines.%20I%20hope%20to%20tackle%20the%20issue%20of%20customer%20safety%20with%20renewed%20resolve%2C%26quot%3B%20Tottori%20said%2C%20per%20The%20Mainichi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETottori's%20appointment%20comes%20after%20JetBlue%20announced%20on%20January%209%20that%20Joanna%20Geraghty%20would%20become%20its%20CEO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fkimelsesser%2F2024%2F01%2F09%2Fjetblue-will-be-the-first-major-us-airline-with-a-female-ceo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecoming%20the%20first%20female%20CEO%20at%20a%20major%20US%20airline.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20Airlines%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-airlines-president-woman-flight-attendant-mitsuko-tottori-profile-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705558469000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a89929dcdb354a98587993%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-airlines-president-woman-flight-attendant-mitsuko-tottori-profile-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mitsuko%20Tottori's%20appointment%20is%20a%20major%20step%20forward%20for%20women%20in%20Japan%2C%20a%20country%20known%20for%20a%20lack%20of%20gender%20equality%20in%20the%20workplace.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mdescalsota%40insider.com%20(Marielle%20Descalsota)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-airlines-president-woman-flight-attendant-mitsuko-tottori-profile-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seven%20killed%20as%20Pakistan%20launches%20airstrikes%20on%20Iran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705558440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-pakistan-sistan-baluchestan_6425241.jpg%3F20240118064721%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fseven-killed-as-pakistan-launches-airstrikes-on-iran-13050660%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%20seven%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20after%20Pakistan%20launched%20airstrikes%20on%20Iranian%20territory%20early%20on%20Thursday%20morning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fseven-killed-as-pakistan-launches-airstrikes-on-iran-13050660%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fseven-killed-as-pakistan-launches-airstrikes-on-iran-13050660%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fseven-killed-as-pakistan-launches-airstrikes-on-iran-13050660%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sundar%20Pichai%20tells%20Google%20to%20expect%20more%20job%20cuts%20in%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705558418000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106948377%2Cimgsize-628919.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fgoogle-ceo-sundar-pichai-confirms-more-layoffs-in-2024-priorities-and-the-year-ahead-memo-to-employees%2Farticleshow%2F106948377.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20confirms%20more%20layoffs%20are%20coming%20as%20the%20company%20has%20tough%20choices%20to%20make.%20Pichai%20also%20said%20that%20not%20all%20teams%20will%20be%20impacted%20but%20jobs%20cut%20might%20happen%20throughout%20the%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fgoogle-ceo-sundar-pichai-confirms-more-layoffs-in-2024-priorities-and-the-year-ahead-memo-to-employees%2Farticleshow%2F106948377.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Decoding%20the%20Indus%20Script%3A%20My%20Findings%20and%20What%20They%20Challenge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18114704%2F1280px-Other_side_of_Moenjodaro_by_Usman_Ghani-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20student%2C%20when%20you%20first%20saw%20images%20of%20the%20ruins%20of%20Harappa%20and%20Mohenjodaro%20in%20history%20textbooks%2C%20your%20teacher%20likely%20told%20you%20that%20deciphering%20the%20signs%20engraved%20on%20the%20tiny%20Indus%20seal%20would%20unveil%20grand%20secrets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20article%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41599-023-02320-7%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESemantic%20scope%20of%20Indus%20inscriptions%20comprising%20taxation%2C%20trade%20and%20craft%20licensing%2C%20commodity%20control%20and%20access%20control%3A%20archaeological%20and%20script-internal%20evidence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20was%20recently%20published%20in%20the%20peer-reviewed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENature%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20group%20journal%20Humanities%20and%20Social%20Sciences%20Communications.%20In%20it%2C%20I%20say%20that%20the%20Indus%20script%20mainly%20encoded%20rules%20and%20information%20about%20ancient%20taxation%2C%20and%20commercial%20licensing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41599-019-0274-1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprevious%20article%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20published%20in%20the%20same%20journal%20back%20in%202019%20says%20that%20Indus%20script%20was%20mainly%20written%20with%20meaning-symbols%2C%20and%20word-symbols%2C%20and%20did%20not%20phonetically%20spell%20out%20words.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20disheartening%20news%20to%20those%20of%20us%20who%20believed%20that%20decoding%20the%20Indus%20script%20would%20mean%20we%20would%20directly%C2%A0%20identify%20the%20languages%20spoken%20in%20the%20Indus%20valley%20civilisation.%20However%2C%20I%20feel%20that%20my%20findings%20about%20the%20nature%20and%20content%20of%20the%20Indus%20script%20do%20not%20take%20away%20the%20possibility%20that%20when%20this%20enigmatic%20script%20will%20speak%20to%20us%2C%20we%20will%20get%20many%20keys%20to%20the%20various%20dimensions%20of%20an%20extremely%20intriguing%20ancient%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20Indus%20script%20signs%20were%20really%20used%20to%20phonetically%20spell%20out%20words%20(they%20are%20not)%2C%20and%20if%20the%20script%20was%20really%20used%20for%20religious%20purposes%2C%20or%20to%20record%20names%20of%20people%20and%20places%2C%20as%20so%20many%20scholars%20have%20wrongly%20imagined%20and%20claimed%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20information%20could%20you%20really%20expect%20to%20extract%20from%20the%20brief%20formulaic%20inscriptions%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20average%20length%20of%20the%20inscriptions%20is%20just%20around%20five%20signs%2C%20if%20you%20consider%20the%20script%20to%20be%20syllabic%20or%20logo-syllabic%2C%20then%20you%20cannot%20reasonably%20expect%20to%20decode%20more%20than%20a%20few%20names%20of%20ancient%20traders%20and%20rulers%2C%20or%20certain%20names%20of%20ancient%20deities%20and%20places.%20How%20could%20such%20names%20of%20people%2C%20places%2C%20and%20deities%20significantly%20enrich%20your%20understanding%20of%20the%20world%20of%20the%20Indus%20valley%20civilisation%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFortunately%2C%20Indus%20script%20signs%20were%20not%20alphabets%20or%20syllables%2C%20and%20did%20not%20merely%20encode%20proper%20names.%20Since%20each%20of%20these%20signs%20symbolically%20encoded%20specific%20meanings%2C%20by%20analysing%20them%2C%20we%20can%20actually%20get%20to%20know%20a%20lot%20more%20about%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Indus%20valley%20civilisation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095431%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.10%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22696%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095431%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.10%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%20696w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095431%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.10%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x54.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693446%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22126%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20of%20these%20signs%20have%20retained%20their%20pictographic%20natures%20(e.g.%2C%20look%20at%20some%20anthropomorphic%20script%20signs%20above%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E).%20Since%20symbols%20are%20deeply%20connected%20with%20the%20culture%20and%20the%20world%20views%20of%20their%20users%2C%20we%20get%20the%20opportunity%20to%20understand%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20ancient%20people%20by%20decoding%20their%20symbols.%20Thus%2C%20each%20Indus%20script%20sign%20has%20a%20rich%20and%20complex%20story%20to%20tell%20us%2C%20offering%20much%20more%20than%20a%20phonetic%20seal-script%20could%20have%20offered.%20Moreover%2C%20since%20we%20got%20our%20hands%20on%20an%20ancient%20mercantile%20script%2C%20its%20decoding%20will%20immensely%20help%20reconstruct%20the%20pre-historical%20economy%2C%20commerce%2C%20and%20material%20culture%20of%20its%20users.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAncient%20scripts%20often%20use%20different%20types%20of%20symbolism.%20For%20example%2C%20certain%20script%20signs%20can%20use%20metonymy%2C%20where%20the%20sign%20may%20resemble%20an%20object%20related%20to%20a%20concept%2C%20to%20signify%20that%20concept.%20Such%20signs%20are%20language%20agnostic%2C%20but%20often%20culture%20specific.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20England%2C%20a%20crown%20usually%20symbolises%20%E2%80%9Cking%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cqueen%E2%80%9D%2C%20whereas%20in%20ancient%20Egypt%2C%20sceptres%20were%20used%20as%20royal%20symbols.%20Many%20of%20the%20Indus%20script%20signs%20were%20such%20language%20agnostic%20meaning-units%20(sematograms)%20which%20either%20directly%20signified%20the%20object%20they%20resembled%2C%20or%20metonymically%20signified%20a%20meaning%20culturally%20associated%20with%20the%20object.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20in%20certain%20cases%2C%20language-specific%20homonymy%20might%20have%20been%20used.%20For%20example%2C%20since%20%E2%80%9Cflour%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cflower%E2%80%9D%20sound%20similar%20in%20English%2C%20if%20someone%20wants%20to%20write%20English%20words%20symbolically%2C%20they%20may%20use%20a%20specific%20flower%E2%80%99s%20image%20to%20signify%20%E2%80%9Cflour%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20it%20is%20more%20difficult%20to%20express%20%E2%80%9Cflour%E2%80%9D%20by%20a%20direct%20symbol.%20Certain%20Indus%20signs%20were%20arguably%20logograms%20that%20used%20such%20homonymy%20and%20other%20linguistic%20symbolisms.%20Thus%2C%20even%20though%20we%20cannot%20directly%20discover%20the%20languages%20of%C2%A0%20the%20Indus%20valley%20civilisation%20by%20decoding%20the%20Indus%20script%2C%20if%20we%20can%20infer%20the%20civilisation%E2%80%99s%20languages%20from%20other%20sources%2C%20then%20certain%20symbolisms%20used%20in%20certain%20Indus%20logograms%20can%20corroborate%20our%20linguistic%20inferences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20based%20on%20various%20archaeological%2C%20historical%2C%20and%20linguistic%20evidence%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41599-021-00868-w%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emy%202021%20article%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20has%20claimed%20that%20languages%20of%20ancestral%20Dravidian%20language%20groups%20were%20spoken%20by%20a%20substantial%20population%20of%20the%20Indus%20civilisation.%20Various%20other%20scholars%20from%20the%20fields%20of%20archaeogenetics%2C%20historical%20linguistics%2C%20ethnoarchaeology%2C%20and%20anthropology%2C%20have%20also%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20linguistic%2C%20cultural%2C%20and%20genetic%20link%20between%20the%20Indus%20people%20and%20the%20present%20speakers%20of%20Dravidian%20languages%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20live%20in%20South%20India.%20Thus%2C%20some%20of%20the%20Indus%20signs%20might%20have%20used%20certain%20ancient%20Dravidian%20symbolism%20that%20can%20also%20be%20traced%20in%20certain%20Proto-Dravidian%20root-words%2C%20and%20their%20homonymic%20usages.%20However%2C%20this%20does%20not%20at%20all%20mean%20that%20people%20of%20other%20speech%20communities%20did%20not%20exist%20in%20the%20one-million%20square%20kilometre%20expanse%20of%20the%20Indus%20civilisation%20(c.%202600%20BC%20to%201900%20BC).%20It%20is%20quite%20possible%20that%20people%20of%20another%20non-Dravidian%20speech%20community%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20use%20their%20symbolism%20for%20a%20commodity%20or%20craft%20they%20specialised%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18113144%2FIndusExampleGraphics.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18113144%2FIndusExampleGraphics.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18113144%2FIndusExampleGraphics-300x144.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18113144%2FIndusExampleGraphics-1024x492.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693460%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20I%20narrate%20the%20novel%20findings%20of%20my%20three%20Nature.com%20articles%20on%20Indus%20script%20and%20languages%2C%20built%20on%20the%20fascinating%20works%20of%20other%20archaeologists%2C%20historians%2C%20and%20linguists%2C%20we%20get%20the%20story%20below%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWas%20Rome%20built%20in%20a%20day%3F%20Neither%20was%20the%20Indus%20valley%20civilisation.%20Even%20in%20the%20early%20Food-Producing%20era%20of%20pre-7000%20to%205500%20BC%20(for%20example%2C%20at%20Mehrgarh)%2C%20the%20ancestors%20of%20Indus%20valley%20civilisation%20did%20not%20only%20excel%20in%20agriculture%20and%20animal%20domestication%2C%20but%20also%20had%20significant%20craft-making%20and%20bartering%20skills.%20For%20example%2C%20they%20made%20exquisite%20gemstone%20and%20shell%20ornaments%20whose%20materials%20were%20procured%20from%20distant%20places.%20During%20the%20Regionalisation%20Era%20(ca.%205500%20to%202600%20BCE)%2C%20various%20rural%20settlements%20in%20the%20Indus%20and%20Ghaggar-Hakra%20river%20valleys%20slowly%20formed%20large%20towns%20and%20market%20areas%2C%20and%20formed%20distinct%20material%20cultures%20and%20craft%20specialisations.%20Then%2C%20in%20the%20Integration%20era%20(c.%202600-1900%20BC)%20of%20this%20most%20expansive%20urban%20civilisation%20of%20the%20Bronze%20age%2C%20there%20was%20extensive%20trading%20and%20communication%20between%20various%20Indus%20settlements%2C%20and%20also%20significant%20trading%20with%20contemporary%20Near%20East%2C%20especially%20ancient%20Persia.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDue%20to%20the%20extremely%20complex%20nature%20of%20Indus%20valley%20civilisation%E2%80%99s%20commerce%2C%20Indus%20elites%20made%20various%20innovations%20in%20their%20commercial%20administrative%20techniques.%20Many%20of%20the%20Indus%20settlements%20possibly%20had%20powerful%20oligarchies%20in%20the%20forms%20of%20merchant%20and%20artisan%20guilds%2C%20who%20were%20either%20directly%20governing%20those%20settlements%2C%20or%20had%20collaborative%20relationships%20with%20local%20or%20regional%20rulers.%20These%20guilds%20and%20region%20based%20governing%20bodies%20needed%20to%20collect%20taxes%20to%20develop%20and%20maintain%20the%20fortified%20settlements%20with%20well-planned%20streets%2C%20drainage%20systems%2C%20water%20management%20systems%20etc.%2C%20made%20available%20as%20public%20goods%20to%20the%20city-residents%2C%20and%20the%20controlled%20and%20secure%20market%20areas%20which%20were%20used%20by%20traders%2C%20farmers%2C%20and%20artisans%20either%20residing%20inside%20the%20fortified%20settlements%2C%20or%20coming%20from%20surrounding%20rural%20or%20semi-urban%20settlements%2C%20and%20distant%20towns.%20The%20elite%20groups%20of%20Indus%20valley%20civilisation%20needed%20to%20standardise%20the%20taxation%20and%20commercial%20licensing%20across%20settlements%2C%20and%20also%20needed%20to%20establish%20value%20relationships%20or%20equivalencies%20between%20various%20commodities%2C%20and%20calculate%20the%20labour%20values%20used%20for%20various%20commercial%20activities%2C%20much%20before%20William%20Petty%2C%20John%20Locke%20or%20Karl%20Marx.%20For%20example%2C%20to%20standardise%20their%20trades%20and%20exchanges%2C%20they%20must%20have%20had%20to%20establish%20how%20much%20barley%20was%20equivalent%20to%20how%20much%20cotton%2C%20or%20silver.%20Mesopotamian%20texts%20provide%20ample%20evidence%20of%20similar%20equivalencies%20and%20standardisations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%20Egyptians%20or%20Mesopotamians%2C%20Indus%20people%20did%20not%20build%20unnecessarily%20extravagant%20monuments.%20They%20loved%20intricately%20made%20miniature%20objects%20of%20art%2C%20and%20intelligently%20constructed%20and%20controlled%20urban%20settlements.%20Similarly%2C%20while%20the%20contemporary%20seals%20of%20ancient%20Near%20East%20were%20often%20used%20to%20authenticate%20individual%20ownerships%20of%20merchandise%20packages%20or%20individual%20officer%E2%80%99s%20endorsements%20of%20legal%20documents%2C%20Indus%20people%20believed%20more%20in%20organisational%20control%2C%20and%20wanted%20to%20write%20information%20related%20to%20taxation%20and%20commercial%20licensing%20on%20their%20organisationally%20controlled%20and%20issued%20seals.%20Now%2C%20the%20ancient%20world%20was%20generally%20more%20multilingual%20than%20today.%20Thus%2C%20there%20were%20surely%20multiple%20languages%2C%20and%20dialects%20across%20the%201%2C000%2C000-km%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%B2%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20span%20of%20the%20Indus%20valley%20civilisation.%20So%2C%20Indus%20elites%20did%20not%20use%20a%20phonetically%20written%20script%20on%20their%20seals%2C%20which%20would%20have%20been%20too%20language-specific%20and%20thus%20unintelligible%20for%20many%20of%20the%20stakeholders.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20they%20had%20certain%20other%20phonetically%20written%20regional%20scripts%20which%20have%20been%20lost%20as%20they%20were%20mainly%20written%20on%20perishable%20materials.%20Even%20the%20highly%20advanced%20Linear%20B%20script%20of%20c.%201400%20BC%20Greece%2C%20written%20mainly%20with%20syllables%20and%20certain%20ideograms%20used%20in%20commercial%20contexts%2C%20has%20been%20found%20only%20from%20a%20few%20palaces%20due%20to%20preservation%20through%20accidental%20fire.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20just%20because%20we%20have%20not%20found%20any%20phonetic%20script%20of%20the%20Indus%20era%20till%20now%2C%20it%20does%20not%20necessarily%20mean%20that%20they%20did%20not%20exist.%20However%2C%20since%20the%20tiny%20Indus%20seals%20were%20not%20used%20to%20write%20names%20of%20people%20or%20places%2C%20such%20phonetic%20scripts%20are%20not%20found%20on%20seals%2C%20the%20same%20way%20we%20do%20not%20find%20poetry%20written%20using%20English%20alphabets%20in%20modern%20documents%20written%20with%20morse%20codes.%20The%20purpose%20of%20a%20document%20decides%20the%20type%20of%20writing%20system%20used%20on%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18125120%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-12.49.1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18125120%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-12.49.1.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18125120%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-12.49.1-300x195.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18125120%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-12.49.1-1024x666.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693485%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20infographic%20summary%20of%20evidences%20that%20Indus%20seals%20and%20tablets%20were%20formalized%20data%20carriers%20used%20in%20commercial%20contexts%20where%20trade-control%2C%20standardisation%20and%20metrology%20played%20important%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndus%20seals%20were%20highly%20standardised%20regarding%20their%20materials%2C%20the%20style%20of%20using%20certain%20animal%20iconographies%20and%20religious%20iconographies%20on%20them%2C%20and%20the%20way%20certain%20signs%20were%20written%20on%20them%20in%20a%20formulaic%20way.%20These%20seals%20are%20seldom%20found%20in%20religious%20contexts.%20The%20iconographies%20of%20various%20animals%20and%20religious%20scenes%20found%20on%20them%20were%20emblems%20of%20their%20issuing%20organizations%2C%20rulers%2C%20or%20governing-bodies.%20However%2C%20just%20because%20religious%20scenes%20are%20carved%20on%20certain%20seals%2C%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20the%20seals%20were%20religious%20amulets.%20If%20we%20use%20the%20iconography%20of%20goddess%20Lakshmi%20on%20some%20of%20our%20currency%20coins%2C%20will%20it%20mean%20that%20the%20coins%20are%20religious%20tokens%3F%20Since%20the%20seals%20were%20not%20properties%20of%20individuals%2C%20and%20were%20not%20primarily%20used%20as%20religious%20amulets%2C%20they%20were%20never%20found%20in%20grave-goods%20unlike%20the%20seals%20of%20the%20ancient%20Near%20East.%20These%20seals%20were%20often%20found%20concentrated%20in%20places%20where%20tax-collection%20and%20commercial%20licensing%20were%20done.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20near%20the%20narrow%20gates%20of%20certain%20fortified%20settlements%2C%20where%20incoming%20and%20outgoing%20packages%20of%20commodities%20were%20examined%2C%20measured%2C%20and%20made%20to%20pay%20taxes%2C%20these%20seals%20are%20found%20with%20other%20tax-collection%20tools%2C%20such%20as%20the%20standardised%20cubical%20weights.%20These%20weights%20were%20used%20for%20tax-collection%2C%20not%20day-to-day%20barter%2C%20as%20established%20by%20archaeologists%20by%20analysing%20their%20distribution%20statistics%20and%20archaeological%20contexts.%20Most%20of%20these%20weights%20were%20less%20than%2060%20grams%20in%20weight%2C%20and%20the%2013.6%20grams%20weight%20was%20the%20most%20popular%20one.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20Indus%20weight%20system%20was%20based%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20gold-measuring%20unit.%20Thus%2C%20these%20weights%20were%20mainly%20used%20to%20collect%20taxes%20in%20the%20form%20of%20precious%20metals%2C%20indicating%20the%20existence%20of%20an%20ancient%20bullion%20standard.%20The%20seals%20often%20accompanied%20such%20weights%20near%20city-gates%2C%20and%20in%20the%20same%20rooms%20of%20ancient%20office%20buildings.%20Such%20seals%20and%20weights%20were%20often%20found%20concentrated%20near%20various%20craft%20workshops%C2%A0%20such%20as%20lapidary%20workshops%20or%20shell%20bangle%20workshops%20in%20several%20settlements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20seal-inscriptions%20had%20various%20commodity-types%2C%20craft-types%2C%20and%20tax%2Flicense-types%20encoded%20by%20various%20types%20of%20signs.%20Often%20certain%20stroke-numerals%20signifying%20craft%2Fcommodity%2Ftrade%20specific%20tax-rates%20and%20license-fees%20were%20mentioned%20before%20the%20commodity%2Fcraft%20signs%20and%20tax%2Flicense%20signs%20(below%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20396px)%2085vw%2C%20396px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095425%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.24%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22396%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095425%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.24%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%20996w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095425%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.24%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x52.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693445%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2269%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20collecting%20tax%20on%20the%20merchandise%20of%20a%20trader%2C%20soft%20clay-tags%20stamped%20with%20inscribed%20seals%20(called%20sealings)%20were%20attached%20to%20the%20merchandise%20to%20indicate%20that%20it%20had%20paid%20a%20specific%20type%20of%20tax%20or%20license-fee%20for%20a%20specific%20type%20of%20commodity%20or%20commercial%20activity%2C%20usings%20a%20specific%20tax%20rate.%20Such%20pieces%20of%20information%20were%20cross%20checked%20at%20different%20imposts%20by%20designated%20officials%2C%20who%20compared%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20packages%20with%20the%20tax-payment%20information%20on%20the%20seal-stamp%20impressions%20attached%20to%20them%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20right%20type%20of%20tax%20was%20paid.%C2%A0%20Occasionally%2C%20the%20modes%20of%20tax%20payment%20(e.g.%2C%20food%20grains%2C%20precious%20metals%2C%20etc.)%20were%20also%20mentioned%20in%20the%20seal-inscriptions.%20Many%20of%20such%20commodity-sealings%2C%20that%20were%20once%20attached%20to%20various%20types%20of%20containers%2C%20and%20were%20later%20preserved%20for%20auditing%2C%20are%20found%20in%20a%20warehouse-like%20structure%20in%20Lothal.%20Commodities%20of%20similar%20taxation%20categories%20were%20possibly%20also%20segregated%20in%20different%20chambers%20of%20such%20warehouses%2C%20as%20the%20inscriptions%20found%20on%20the%20commodity%20sealings%2C%20are%20also%20found%20on%20certain%20room-locking%20mechanisms%20sealed%20with%20similar%20inscriptions.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20around%20200%20years%20of%20establishing%20the%20seal-based%20administration%2C%20certain%20miniature%20tablets%20were%20introduced%20which%20were%20used%20parallely%20and%20were%20closely%20related%20to%20the%20seals%2C%20as%20the%20obverse%20sides%20of%20these%20tablets%20mentioned%20identical%20or%20similar%20commercial%20records%20that%20are%20found%20on%20seals.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20495px)%2085vw%2C%20495px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095417%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.34%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22495%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095417%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.34%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%20882w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095417%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.34%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x50.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693444%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2282%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reverse%20sides%20of%20these%20tablets%20however%20mainly%20contained%20certain%20numerical%20and%20metrological%20notations%20(above%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20where%20the%20rimless-jar-like%20sign%20possibly%20represented%20a%20volumetric%20measurement%20used%20in%20license-fee%20collection%2C%20and%20metonymically%20signified%20corresponding%20licenses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20404px)%2085vw%2C%20404px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095410%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.40%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22404%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095410%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.40%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1.png%20642w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095410%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.40%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1-300x68.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693443%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2292%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20numerical%20signs%20preceding%20the%20rimless-jar-sign%C2%A0%20signified%20certain%20fixed%20licence-fees%20and%20licence-slabs.%20Often%20the%20same%20obverse%20inscriptions%20related%20to%20specific%20commercial%20activities%20and%20taxes%20(above)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewere%20applied%20to%20different%20license-slabs%2C%20such%20as%20below%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20378px)%2085vw%2C%20378px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095402%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.44%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22378%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095402%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.44%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%20896w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18095402%2FScreenshot-2024-01-18-at-9.37.44%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x52.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693442%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2265%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20is%20functionally%20comparable%20to%20modern%20licensing%20systems.%20For%20example%2C%C2%A0%20the%20food-producing%20companies%20of%20modern%20India%20have%20to%20pay%20license-fees%20according%20to%20different%20license%20slabs%20based%20on%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20food-producing%20capacity%2C%20amount%20of%20revenue%2C%20and%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20license.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Localisation%20Era%20(%20after%201900%20BCE%20to%201300%20BCE)%2C%20when%20the%20decline%20of%20Indus%20economico-political%20units%20happened%20(for%20contentious%20reasons)%2C%20it%20wiped%20out%20Indus%20valley%20civilisation%E2%80%99s%20large-scale%20organised%20trade%2C%20and%20related%20taxation%20and%20trade-controlling%20devices%2C%20such%20as%20seals%2C%20tablets%2C%20and%20standardised%20cubical%20weights.%20This%20can%20be%20compared%20to%20the%20demise%20of%20the%20inscribed%20%E2%80%9CBala%E2%80%9D%20taxation%20tablets%20of%20ancient%20Mesopotamia%2C%20which%20disappeared%20after%20the%20UR%20state%20and%20its%20taxation%20system%20dissolved%20under%20the%20attack%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CMartu%E2%80%9D%20tribes.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20tax%20collection%20system%20and%20use%20of%20tax-seals%20mentioned%20in%20Kautilya%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EArtha%C5%9B%C4%81stra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20400%20BC%20have%20various%20similarities%20with%20the%20Indus%20taxation%20system%20reconstructed%20from%20archaeological%20and%20script-internal%20evidence%2C%20and%20arguably%20have%20an%20ancient%20Indus%20root%2C%20which%20got%20much%20more%20advanced%2C%20customised%2C%20and%20canonised%20by%20the%20Mauryan%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHave%20I%20decoded%20the%20Indus%20script%20yet%3F%20Yes%2C%20I%20claim%20to%20have%20partly%20decoded%20Indus%20script.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20claim%20this%20as%20I%20have%20decoded%20its%20main%20mechanism%20of%20conveying%20meanings%3B%20the%20type%20of%20meanings%20encoded%20by%20it%2C%20i.e.%2C%20its%20semantic%20scope%3B%20the%20type%20of%20information%20encoded%20by%20its%20different%20segments%20and%20sign-classes%3B%20and%20the%20specific%20meanings%20of%20a%20few%20Indus%20script%20signs.%20Some%20of%20the%20decoding%20are%20already%20published%20and%20presented%20in%20various%20seminars%2C%20while%20the%20others%20are%20being%20peer-reviewed%2C%20or%20are%20being%20written%20in%20the%20forms%20of%20articles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBahata%20Ansumali%20Mukhopadhyay%20is%20a%20software%20professional%20and%20an%20independent%20researcher.%20She%20researches%20the%20structural%20and%20semantic%20aspects%20of%20Indus%20script%20inscriptions%20and%20explores%20the%20linguistic%20identities%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Indus%20Valley%20civilisation.%C2%A0%20She%20is%20a%20Bengali%20poet.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20author%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20her%20senior%20colleague%20Hemant%20Shergare%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20software%20at%20Infor%20Inc.%2C%20and%20her%20father%2C%20Professor%20Amartya%20Mukhopadhyay%2C%20without%20whose%20moral%20support%20and%20encouragement%2C%20she%20would%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20continue%20her%20lonely%20journey%20in%20the%20Indus%20valley.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705558399000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18114704%2F1280px-Other_side_of_Moenjodaro_by_Usman_Ghani-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fdecoding-the-indus-script-my-findings-and-what-they-challenge%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Have%20I%20decoded%20the%20Indus%20script%20yet%3F%20Partly.%20Does%20it%20reveal%20all%20that%20it%20was%20touted%20to%20reveal%3F%20We%20shall%20find%20out.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fdecoding-the-indus-script-my-findings-and-what-they-challenge%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%3A%20Jats%20of%20Bharatpur%2C%20Dholpur%20Launch%20Stir%20Seeking%20OBC%20Quota%20at%20the%20Central%20Level%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18112909%2FEffect-70.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Jats%20of%20Bharatpur%20and%20Dholpur%20in%20Rajasthan%20have%20once%20again%20hit%20the%20streets%20demanding%20their%20inclusion%20in%20the%20central%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20Jats%20began%20their%20protest%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20January%2017%2C%20at%20Jaicholi%20village%20in%20Bharatpur%20district%20and%20vowed%20to%20continue%20it%20indefinitely%20if%20their%20demands%20are%20not%20met.%20The%20Rajasthan%20government%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20sent%20platoons%20of%20police%20forces%20to%20the%20protest%20site%20to%20quell%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInclusion%20in%20the%20central%20OBC%20list%20would%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20reservation%20for%20the%20community%20in%20central%20jobs%20and%20centrally-run%20educational%20institutions.%20The%20protestors%20issued%20an%20ultimatum%20of%20January%2022%20to%20the%20authorities%20to%20meet%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTill%20January%2022%2C%20we%20will%20protest%20in%20a%20Gandhian%20way.%20If%20the%20government%20does%20not%20fulfill%20our%20demands%2C%20then%20we%20will%20intensify%20the%20movement%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bharatpur-Dholpur%20Jat%20Aarakshan%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%20convenor%20Nem%20Singh%20Faujdar%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjats-protest-in-rajasthan-over-inclusion-in-central-other-backward-classes-list-4881998%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJats%20of%20Bharatpur%20and%20Dholpur%20began%20their%20demand%20for%20OBC%20reservation%20first%20in%201998.%20In%202013%2C%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20granted%20OBC%20reservations%20to%20the%20Jats%20in%20Bharatpur%2C%20Dholpur%2C%20and%20nine%20other%20states.%20However%2C%20after%20the%20Modi%20government%20assumed%20power%20in%202014%2C%20the%20Centre%20annulled%20that%20reservation%2C%20enabled%20through%20OBC%20quota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20March%202015%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20also%20excluded%20them%20from%20the%20Central%20OBC%20list%2C%20and%20subsequently%2C%20they%20were%20removed%20from%20the%20state%20OBC%20list%20after%20a%20high%20court%20verdict%20in%20August%202015.%20Those%20who%20oppose%20awarding%20of%20OBC%20quota%20to%20them%20argue%20that%20they%20had%20historical%20ties%20to%20the%20former%20royal%20family%20in%20these%20districts%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20Jat%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20things%20changed%20once%20again%2C%20when%2C%20in%20August%202017%2C%20the%20Vasundhara%20Raje-led%20BJP%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%20granted%20reservations%20once%20again%20to%20Jats%20of%20the%20two%20districts.%20Now%2C%20they%20are%20demanding%20for%20their%20inclusion%20in%20the%20Central%20OBC%20List%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705558212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18112909%2FEffect-70.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frajasthan-jats-