ry%2021.%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20directed%20the%20registry%20to%20seek%20orders%20from%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20to%20constitute%20a%20bench%20with%20Justice%20Ujjal%20Bhuiyan%20to%20hear%20the%20petitions%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20petitions%2C%20the%20three%20men%20cited%20reasons%20ranging%20from%20family%20weddings%20and%20dependent%20parents%20to%20the%20harvest%20season%20for%20requesting%20more%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20verdict%20on%20January%208%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20cancelled%20the%20Gujarat%20government's%20decision%20to%20grant%20remission%20to%20the%2011%20men%20who%20gang-raped%20Bilkis%20Bano%20and%20murdered%20seven%20members%20of%20her%20family%2C%20including%20her%20three-year%20old%20daughter%2C%20during%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20riots.%20The%20judges%20also%20directed%20the%20convicts%2C%20who%20were%20released%20on%20Independence%20Day%20in%202022%2C%20to%20surrender%20by%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConvict%20Govindbhai%20Nai%20has%20asked%20for%20four%20more%20weeks%20and%20Ramesh%20Chandana%20and%20Mitesh%20Bhatt%20have%20sought%20six%20more%20weeks%20to%20turn%20themselves%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Nai%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20barber%2C%20claims%20that%20he%20is%20the%20sole%20caregiver%20for%20his%2088-year-old%20bedridden%20father%20and%2075-year-old%20mother%2C%20who%20he%20says%20are%20completely%20dependent%20on%20him.%20He%20also%20says%20he%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20financial%20needs%20of%20his%20two%20children.%20The%2055-year-old%20also%20referred%20to%20his%20own%20health%2C%20saying%20he%20has%20asthma%20and%20%C2%A0recently%20underwent%20a%20surgery.%20Nai%20also%20claims%20that%20after%20his%20release%20from%20prison%2C%20he%20had%20not%20violated%20any%20law%20and%20had%20complied%20with%20the%20terms%20and%20conditions%20of%20the%20release%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERame