%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20head%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20found%20a%20parallel%20for%20Rohit%20in%20R.%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20did%20a%20similar%20tactical%20swap%20during%20an%20IPL%202022%20match%20between%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20and%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20Ash-level%20thinking.%20Taking%20himself%20out%20was%20Ash-level%20thinking%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dravid%20told%20the%20host%20broadcaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDravid%3A%20That%20was%20Ashwin's%20level%20of%20thinking%20(about%20Rohit's%20Retired%20out)%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAFGvsIND%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23AFGvsIND%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FINDvsAFG%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23INDvsAFG%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FRohitSharma%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23RohitSharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FRohitSharma%25F0%2593%2583%25B5%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23RohitSharma%F0%93%83%B5%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAshwin%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOrROVyQfo9%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOrROVyQfo9%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Illaya%20Bharathi%20(%40bharathi_illaya)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbharathi_illaya%2Fstatus%2F1747686476937388431%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Afghanistan%20coach%20Jonathan%20Trott%20hinted%20at%20minimal%20communication%20between%20officials%20and%20the%20players%20as%20the%20whole%20episode%20panned%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20no%20idea%20(whether%20Rohit%20retired%20hurt%20or%20out).%20Has%20there%20ever%20been%20two%20Super%20Overs%3F%20That's%20what%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20say.%20We%20keep%20setting%20these%20new%20rules.%20What%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20say%20is%20we%20kept%20testing%20the%20rules%2C%20we%20kept%20testing%20the%20guidelines%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Trott%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrott%20stressed%20his%20point%20saying%20that%20the%20rule%20about%20the%20use%20of%20bowlers%20in%20Super%20Overs%20too%20was%20not%20conveyed%20to%20them%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfghanistan%20wanted%20to%20use%20Azmatullah%20Omarzai%20in%20the%20second%20Super%20Over%20but%20since%20the%20pacer%20had%20already%20bowled%20the%20first%20Super%20Over%2C%20he%20was%20ineligible%20to%20operate%20a%20second%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20communicated%20(the%20rule).%20We%20wanted%20Azmat%20to%20bowl%20the%20second%20over%20again%2C%20but%20Fareed%20(Ahmad)%20bowled%20a%20great%20over.%20But%20these%20things%20will%20be%20explained%20and%20done%20in%20writing%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20those%20are%20the%20rules%2C%20that's%20great.%20I%20just%20think%20we%20had%20a%20good%20game%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20(rules)%20should%20be%20the%20talking%20point%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Trott%2C%20an%20experienced%20coach%20and%20a%20former%20player%20of%20repute%2C%20might%20just%20have%20forgotten%20that%20the%20Super%20Over%20rules%20are%20in%20vogue%20since%202019%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20an%20external%20entity%20to%20send%20reminders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20another%20flash%20point%20in%20the%20game%20when%20Afghan%20batters%20Mohammed%20Nabi%20and%20Rahmanullah%20Gurbaz%20ran%20three%20runs%20after%20wicketkeeper%20Sanju%20Samson's%20throw%20deflected%20off%20Nabi's%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20helped%20Afghanistan%20to%20score%2016%20in%20the%20first%20Super%20Over.%20But%20Rohit%20was%20quick%20to%20express%20his%20displeasure%20to%20Nabi%20and%20the%20umpires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Dravid%20did%20not%20fuss%20too%20much%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20part%20of%20the%20game.%20There%20will%20be%20some%20frustrations%20and%20at%20times%20things%20happen%2C%20but%20it's%20okay.%20Obviously%2C%20the%20ball%20hit%20the%20non-striker%2C%20and%20then%20it%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20first%20T20%2C%20I%20think%20the%20ball%20hit%20the%20back%20of%20one%20of%20our%20batsmen%20and%20we%20ran%20as%20well.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20there's%20nothing%20to%20read%20into%20it.%20Nothing%20in%20the%20rules%20stops%20you%20from%20running%20those%20runs.%20So%2C%20that's%20fine%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705553400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fstonlki_rahul-dravid_625x300_18_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-afghanistan-t20i-2024%2Fashwin-level-thinking-rahul-dravids-reaction-on-rohit-sharmas-super-over-call-is-viral-4883944%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rahul%20Dravid%20hailed%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20Super%20Over%20decision%20to%20'retired%20out'%20in%20the%203rd%20T20I%20against%20Afghanistan%2C%20calling%20it%20'Ravichandran%20Ashwin-level%20thinking'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taiwan's%20remaining%20Pacific%20allies%20pledge%20support%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705553380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106946214%2Cimgsize-1303308.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwans-remaining-pacific-allies-pledge-support%2Farticleshow%2F106945944.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106945944.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETaiwan's%20remaining%20Pacific%20Island%20allies%20have%20offered%20their%20support%20following%20Nauru's%20decision%20to%20cut%20ties%2C%20just%20days%20after%20a%20presidential%20election%2C%20reducing%20Taiwan's%20diplomatic%20footprint%20in%20the%20area%20to%20three%20countries.%20With%20Nauru's%20departure%2C%20Taiwan's%20regional%20allies%20have%20been%20reduced%20from%20six%20to%20three%20since%202019%2C%20despite%20heightened%20US-China%20rivalry%20for%20security%20relations%20and%20offers%20of%20infrastructure%20and%20financing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwans-remaining-pacific-allies-pledge-support%2Farticleshow%2F106945944.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwans-remaining-pacific-allies-pledge-support%2Famp_articleshow%2F106945944.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwans-remaining-pacific-allies-pledge-support%2Famp_articleshow%2F106945944.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIM%20Calcutta%20Removes%20Director%20Sahadeb%20Sarkar%20Over%20Sexual%20Harassment%20Complaint%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F13132528%2FIIM-Calcutta-Auditorium.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20Calcutta%20(IIM-C)%20has%20removed%20its%20director-in-charge%2C%20Sahadeb%20Sarkar%2C%20because%20of%20an%20allegation%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20him.%20The%20institute%20announced%20this%20decision%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday%20(January%2016).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Internal%20Complaints%20Committee%20(ICC)%20of%20the%20institute%20has%20been%20in%20receipt%20of%20a%20written%20complaint%20under%20the%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20(Prevention%2C%20Prohibition%20and%20Redressal)%20Act%2C%202013%20(POSH%20Act)%20against%20the%20then%20Director-in-Charge%20professor%20Sahadeb%20Sarkar.%20The%20ICC%20has%20ascertained%20that%20prima%20facie%20the%20complaint%20warrants%20a%20formal%20inquiry%20and%20communicated%20the%20same%20to%20the%20Board%20of%20Governors%20(BoG)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIIM-C%20Board%20of%20Governors%20held%20a%20special%20meeting%20on%206%20January%202024%20and%20accepted%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20ICC%20that%20professor%20Sahadeb%20Sarkar%20shall%20not%20continue%20in%20the%20office%20of%20Director-in-Charge%20and%20shall%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20said%20post%20and%20any%20other%20position%20wherein%20he%20has%20administrative%20charges%20in%20IIM%20Calcutta%2C%20during%20the%20pendency%20of%20formal%20inquiry%20before%20the%20ICC%20and%20any%20proceedings%20arising%20therefrom%20or%20incidental%20thereto%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fkolkata%2Fiim-calcutta-removes-director-over-sexual-harassment-complaint-9112870%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20next%20senior-most%20faculty%20member%2C%20professor%20Saibal%20Chattopadhyay%2C%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20director-in-charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarkar%20is%20the%20third%20IIM%20director%20in%20three%20years%20to%20leave%20before%20his%20term%20is%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarkar%20has%20called%20the%20allegations%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fdirector-in-charge-sahadeb-sarkar-removed-over-sexual-harassment-case-iim-calcutta%2Fcid%2F1994256%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20%E2%80%9CI%20emphatically%20deny%20the%20allegations%20made%20against%20me.%20I%20am%20shocked%20with%20the%20baseless%20allegations.%20In%20any%20case%20this%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20official%20press%20release%20by%20the%20management%20and%20I%20am%20prevented%20from%20speaking%20to%20the%20press%20by%20the%20POSH%20rules%2017(6)%20of%20the%20institute.%20I%20will%20address%20this%20appropriately%20at%20an%20appropriate%20forum%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705553109000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F13132528%2FIIM-Calcutta-Auditorium.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fiim-calcutta-removes-director-sahadeb-sarkar-over-sexual-harassment-complaint%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20next%20senior-most%20faculty%20member%2C%20professor%20Saibal%20Chattopadhyay%2C%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20director-in-charge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fiim-calcutta-removes-director-sahadeb-sarkar-over-sexual-harassment-complaint%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20next%20country%20to%20land%20humans%20on%20the%20moon%20in%20the%20next%2010%20years%20'sets%20a%20precedent'%20for%20who%20decides%20the%20rules%20there%3A%20US%20officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225691%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22China's%20Chang'e-4%20lunar%20probe%2C%20taken%20by%20the%20Yutu-2%20moon%20rover%2C%20on%20the%20far%20side%20of%20the%20moon.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a8a7886979d737182433ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223179%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChina's%20Chang'e-4%20lunar%20probe%2C%20taken%20by%20the%20Yutu-2%20moon%20rover%2C%20on%20the%20far%20side%20of%20the%20moon.%3Cp%3EChina%20National%20Space%20Administration%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMore%20than%2050%20years%20since%20Neil%20Armstrong%20landed%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20the%20world%20is%20racing%20to%20the%20lunar%20surface%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENASA%20was%20slated%20to%20land%20astronauts%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%20earlier%20than%20China%20but%20has%20announced%20delays.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECongressional%20leaders%20on%20Wednesday%20fretted%20that%20China%20could%20land%20first%20and%20become%20a%20space%20power.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECongressional%20leaders%20on%20Wednesday%20warned%20of%20consequences%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20may%20face%20if%20they%20lose%20the%20new%20race%20to%20the%20moon%2C%20as%20the%20National%20American%20Space%20Agency%20announced%20delays%20to%20its%20crewed%20Artemis%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20worries%20were%20largely%20directed%20at%20efforts%20by%20China%20to%20forge%20its%20own%20space%20dominance%20and%20land%20astronauts%20on%20the%20moon%20in%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20is%20actively%20soliciting%20international%20partners%20for%20a%20lunar%20mission%2C%20a%20lunar%20research%20station%2C%20and%20has%20stated%20its%20ambition%20to%20have%20human%20astronauts%20on%20the%20surface%20by%202030%2C%26quot%3B%20Rep.%20Frank%20Lucas%20of%20Oklahoma%20said%20at%20a%20Science%2C%20Space%2C%20and%20Technology%20House%20Committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP3ZFqd4DNlk%26ab_channel%3DHouseScience%252CSpace%252CandTechnologyCommittee%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20about%20the%20Artemis%20project.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20country%20that%20lands%20first%20will%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20set%20a%20precedent%20for%20whether%20future%20lunar%20activities%20are%20conducted%20with%20openness%20and%20transparency%2C%20or%20in%20a%20more%20restricted%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lucas%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20other%20House%20representatives%20said%20they%20were%20concerned%20by%20the%20delays%20from%20NASA%2C%20which%20said%20on%20January%209%20that%20its%20Artemis%202%20launch%20%E2%80%94%20which%20aims%20to%20send%20US%20astronauts%20to%20the%20moon%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20postponed%20from%20November%202024%20to%20September%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENASA%20wants%20to%20fix%20issues%20before%20launch%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-artemis-megarocket-launches-orion-spaceship-toward-moon-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArtemis%20missions%3C%2Fa%3E%20comprise%20NASA's%20modern%20attempt%20to%20return%20to%20the%20moon%2C%20more%20than%2050%20years%20since%20Neil%20Armstrong%20first%20stepped%20foot%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20first%20launch%20was%20an%20uncrewed%20test%20flight%20in%202022%2C%20while%20its%20second%20launch%2C%20now%20scheduled%20for%202025%2C%20will%20send%20four%20astronauts%20around%20the%20moon%20but%20not%20on%20it.%20A%20third%20mission%2C%20now%20delayed%20from%202025%20to%20September%202026%2C%20would%20finally%20put%20American%20crews%20on%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENASA%20said%20it's%20had%20to%20delay%20the%20missions%20because%20it%20first%20needs%20to%20fix%20issues%20with%20its%20spacecraft's%20heat%20shield%2C%20which%20protects%20crews%20from%20extreme%20temperatures%20as%20they%20re-enter%20Earth's%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20agency%20said%20it's%20also%20working%20on%20problems%20with%20the%20craft's%20life%20support%20system%20and%20emergency%20ejection%20system%2C%20which%20jettisons%20the%20crew%20capsule%20away%20from%20the%20rocket%20if%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20Free%2C%20associate%20administrator%20at%20NASA%2C%20said%20at%20the%20delay%20announcement%20that%20safety%20is%20the%20agency's%20%26quot%3Bnumber%20one%20priority.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20will%20launch%20when%20we%20are%20ready%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mike%20Griffin%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20of%20NASA%2C%20cast%20doubt%20on%20the%20agency's%20prediction%20that%20it%20could%20launch%20its%20man-on-the-moon%20mission%20in%20September%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Artemis%20circumlunar%20mission%20is%2C%20I%20think%2C%20very%20doable%20on%20the%20timescale%20that%20NASA%20has%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Griffin%2C%20who%20was%20NASA%20administrator%20from%202005%20to%202009.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20Artemis%203%2C%20the%20landing%20mission%2C%20is%20at%20all%20realistically%20scheduled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELawmakers%20foresee%20doom%20if%20China%20wins%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECongressional%20leaders%20on%20Wednesday%20acknowledged%20safety%20as%20a%20priority%20but%20repeatedly%20expressed%20nervousness%20over%20the%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20no%20secret%20that%20China%20has%20a%20goal%20to%20surpass%20the%20United%20States%20by%202045%20as%20global%20leaders%20in%20space.%20We%20can't%20allow%20this%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20GOP%20Rep.%20Rich%20McCormick%20of%20Georgia%20said.%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20leading%20edge%20that%20we%20have%20in%20space%20technology%20will%20protect%20the%20United%20States.%20Not%20just%20the%20economy%2C%20but%20technologies%20that%20can%20benefit%20humankind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhoever%20controls%20space%20will%20control%20the%20destiny%20of%20this%20Earth%2C%26quot%3B%20Republican%20Rep.%20Bill%20Posey%20of%20Florida%20said%2C%20calling%20space%20the%20%26quot%3Bultimate%20military%20high%20ground.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20support%20Artemis%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Democratic%20Rep.%20Zoe%20Lofgren%20of%20California.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20want%20it%20to%20be%20successful%2C%20especially%20with%20China%20at%20our%20heels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENASA%2C%20however%2C%20has%20said%20that%20even%20with%20the%20delays%2C%20it%20should%20be%20comfortably%20ahead%20of%20China's%20national%20space%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20China%20has%20a%20very%20aggressive%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20NASA%20Administrator%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.space.com%2Fus-beat-china-to-moon-artemis-nasa-bill-nelson%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20Nelson%20said%20on%20January%209%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20would%20like%20to%20land%20before%20us%20because%20that%20might%20give%20them%20some%20PR%20coup.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20I%20don't%20think%20they%20will.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20intends%20to%20be%20the%20second%20country%2C%20with%20the%20US%20being%20the%20first%20and%20so%20far%20only%2C%20to%20land%20astronauts%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20as%20part%20of%20its%20push%20to%20become%20a%20significant%20space%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fscience%2Farticle%2F3218340%2Fchinas-moon-ambitions-take-shape-construction-road-map-research-station%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestablish%20a%20lunar%20base%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20moon's%20south%20pole%20by%202040%20and%20have%20it%20fully%20operational%20by%202050.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20lead-up%20to%20the%20lunar%20base%20involves%20crewed%20flights%20to%20the%20moon%20via%20its%20Chang'e%20missions%2C%20which%20China%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fscience%2Farticle%2F3218340%2Fchinas-moon-ambitions-take-shape-construction-road-map-research-station%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopened%20to%20international%20collaboration%20in%20October%202023.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20firmly%20believe%20that%20the%20spring%20of%20China's%20space%20science%20has%20arrived%2C%20and%20we%20have%20the%20determination%2C%20confidence%2C%20and%20ability%20to%20resolutely%20complete%20the%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Maj.%20Gen.%20Jing%20Haipeng%2C%20a%20Chinese%20astronaut%20serving%20as%20a%20mission%20commander%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fchina-space-program-moon-368d45fa997307ae2c94bcd7e066e2b4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20the%20Associated%20Press.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENelson%2C%20the%20NASA%20chief%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F01%2F01%2Fwe-better-watch-out-nasa-boss-sounds-alarm-on-chinese-moon-ambitions-00075803%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Politico%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%202023%20that%20the%20world%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20watch%20out%26quot%3B%20for%20China's%20spacefaring%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20fact%3A%20We're%20in%20a%20space%20race%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-country-land-moon-precedent-rules-china-us-artemis-nasa-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705553049000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a8a7b6dcdb354a98587a2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-country-land-moon-precedent-rules-china-us-artemis-nasa-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20and%20China%20are%20racing%20to%20be%20the%20first%20to%20put%20a%20man%20on%20the%20moon%20in%20the%2021st%20Century%2C%20but%20NASA%20last%20week%20announced%20delays%20to%20its%20crewed%20missions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-country-land-moon-precedent-rules-china-us-artemis-nasa-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shilpa%20on%20why%20she%20wants%20to%20reunite%20with%20Akshay%22%2C%22conte