0Rinku%20came%20out%20to%20bat%2C%20having%20lost%204%20batters%20at%20the%20score%20of%2022%20runs%20but%20the%20duo%20remained%20unbeaten%20till%20the%20end%20of%20the%20innings%2C%20guiding%20the%20team%20to%20a%20total%20of%20212%20runs%2C%20capping%20off%20the%20innings%20by%20scoring%2036%20runs%20in%20the%20final%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20slammed%20121%20runs%20off%2069%20balls%20with%2011%20fours%20and%20eight%20sixes%20while%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Rinku%20played%20an%20unbeaten%20knock%20of%2069%20runs%20from%2039%20balls%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20six%20sixes%20in%20his%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cstrong%3EFull%20List%20of%20Records%20India%20shattered%20in%20double%20Super%20Over%20win%20against%20Afghanistan%20in%203rd%20T20I%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHighest%20T20I%20partnership%20for%20any%20wicket%20for%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20and%20Rinku%20stitched%20together%20an%20unbeaten%20partnership%20of%20190%20runs%20against%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E190*%20R%20Sharma%20-%20R%20Singh%20v%20Afg%20Bengaluru%202024%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E176%20S%20Samson%20-%20D%20Hooda%20v%20Ire%20Dublin%202022%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E165%20R%20Sharma%20-%20KL%20Rahul%20v%20SL%20Indore%202017%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E165%20Y%20Jaiswal%20-%20S%20Gill%20v%20WI%20Lauderhill%202023%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHighest%20individual%20scores%20for%20India%20in%20T20Is%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERohit%20Sharma's%20highest%20score%20in%20a%20T20I%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20121*%20is%20the%20highest%20for%20the%20captain%20in%20the%20shortest%20format%20for%20India%2C%20but%20the%20fourth-highest%20individual%20score%20for%20India%20in%20T20Is.%20The%20list%20is%20led%20by%20Shubman%20Gill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E126*%20Shubman%20Gill%20v%20NZ%20Ahmedabad%202023%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E123*%20Ruturaj%20Gai