.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Rinku%20Singh%20and%20his%20partnership%20of%20190%20runs%20with%20him%2C%20Rohit%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCreating%20the%20partnership%20was%20important%20and%20we%20(Rinku%20and%20I)%20kept%20talking%20to%20each%20other%20to%20not%20lose%20that%20intent%20in%20big%20games%20and%20it%20was%20a%20good%20game%20for%20us%20to%20be%20in%2C%20the%20pressure%20was%20there%20and%20was%20important%20to%20bat%20long%20and%20deep%20and%20not%20compromise%20on%20the%20intent%20we%20want%20to%20show.%20The%20last%20couple%20of%20series%20that%20he%20played%2C%20he%20showed%20what%20he%20can%20do%20with%20the%20bat.%20Very%20calm%20and%20knows%20his%20strength%20pretty%20well.%20He%20is%20coming%20of%20age%20and%20doing%20what%20is%20expected%20of%20him%20and%20he%20has%20done%20well%20for%20India.%20It%20augurs%20well%20for%20the%20team%20moving%20forward%2C%20wanted%20someone%20like%20that%20at%20the%20backend%20and%20we%20know%20what%20he%20has%20done%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20he%20has%20carried%20that%20to%20the%20Indian%20colours%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%2015%20games%20and%2011%20innings%20in%20T20Is%20for%20India%2C%20Rinku%20has%20scored%20356%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2089.00%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20176%20with%20two%20half-centuries.%20He%20has%20been%20making%20a%20name%20for%20himself%20as%20a%20finisher%20for%20Men%20in%20Blue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20India%20opted%20to%20bat%20first%20and%20was%20reduced%20to%2022%2F4.%20Following%20this%2C%20Rohit%20(121*%20in%2069%20balls%20with%2011%20fours%20and%20eight%20sixes)%20and%20Rinku%20(69*%20in%2039%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20six%20sixes)%20took%20India%20to%20212%2F4%20in%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFareed%20Ahmed%20(3%2F20)%20was%20the%20best%20bowler%20for%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run%20chase%2C%20Gurbaz%20(50%20in%2032%20balls%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)