0can%20come%20across%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20It%E2%80%99s%20large%2C%20rural%2C%20overwhelmingly%20white%20and%20distinctly%20conservative.%20Pigs%20outnumber%20people%20there%20by%20seven-to-one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIowa%20is%20unusual%20among%20American%20states%20in%20having%20not%20simply%20a%20primary%20election%20to%20help%20determine%20who%20stands%20in%20November%20but%20a%20caucus.%20Only%20Republican%20supporters%20can%20take%20part.%20And%20they%20have%20to%20turn-up%20at%20a%20local%20get-together%2C%20held%20at%20a%20school%20or%20library%2C%20and%20listen%20to%20arguments%20put%20forward%20by%20supporters%20of%20the%20various%20candidates%20before%20casting%20a%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20turn%20up%20late%2C%20or%20don%E2%80%99t%20stay%20until%20the%20end%2C%20your%20choice%20might%20not%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIowa%20accounts%20for%20not%20quite%201%25%20of%20America%E2%80%99s%20population%3B%20and%20only%20one-in-thirty%20Iowans%20took%20part%20in%20the%20Republican%20caucus.%20So%20not%20quite%20100%2C000%20Iowans%20are%20making%20the%20weather%20in%20a%20contest%20to%20decide%20who%20governs%20a%20nation%20of%20more%20than%20330%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20Iowa%20are%20used%20to%20harsh%20winters%2C%20but%20the%20white-out%20which%20descended%20on%20the%20state%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20was%20something%20different%20%E2%80%93%20pushing%20temperatures%20down%20to%20ten%20degrees%20below%20zero%20(much%20lower%20when%20wind%20chill%20is%20taken%20into%20account).%20No%20wonder%20that%20turn-out%20was%20lower%20than%20usual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESnow%20piles%20taller%20than%20people%20in%20Ankeny%2C%20Iowa%20on%20caucus%20day%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbkfEchH5cl%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbkfEchH5cl%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jill%20Colvin%20(%40colvinj)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcolvinj%2Fstatus%2F1746981545250877505%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2015%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20American%20politics%20is%20entering%20a%20new%20Ice%20Age.%20It%E2%80%99s%20frozen%20in%20the%20past.%20Donald%20Trump%20seems%20set%20to%20be%20the%20Republican%20candidate%20for%20a%20third%20successive%20presidential%20election%3B%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20says%20he%20is%20determined%20to%20stand%20again%20in%20spite%20of%20his%20age%20(he%E2%80%99s%2081)%2C%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20Democratic%20ticket%2C%20as%20presidential%20or%20vice-presidential%20contender%2C%20for%20the%20fourth%20time%20in%20five%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerica%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20seems%20to%20have%20lost%20the%20ability%20to%20renew%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20tipped%20to%20win%20handsomely%20in%20Iowa%2C%20but%20taking%20more%20than%20half%20the%20total%20vote%20in%20the%20caucus%20is%20an%20emphatic%20triumph.%20His%20two%20main%20challengers%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67989135%5C%22%3ERon%20DeSantis%20took%20second%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20narrowly%20ahead%20of%20Nikki%20Haley%20(born%20Nimrata%20Randhawa%20to%20Punjabi%20parents%20who%20emigrated%20to%20the%20US%20in%20the%201960s)%20%E2%80%93%20are%20not%20only%20a%20long%20way%20behind%2C%20but%20destined%20to%20continue%20sniping%20at%20each%20other%20to%20secure%20the%20mantle%20of%20principal%20challenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy%2C%20a%20biotech%20entrepreneur%20whose%20parents%20were%20migrants%20to%20the%20US%20from%20Kerala%2C%20came%20a%20poor%20fourth%20in%20the%20caucus%20and%20has%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20race.%20He%20has%20endorsed%20his%20fellow%20conservative%2C%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20battleground%20now%20shifts%20to%20the%20much%20more%20liberal%20state%20of%20Ne