of%20apparent%20confusion.%20Most%20Americans%2C%20opinion%20polls%20suggest%2C%20think%20Biden%20is%20too%20old%20to%20serve%20as%20president%20for%20another%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20seems%20to%20have%20convinced%20himself%20that%20only%20he%20can%20frustrate%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20ambition%20to%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%20Democrats%20believe%20that%20a%20second%20Trump%20presidency%20could%20imperil%20America%E2%80%99s%20democracy.%20But%20it%20could%20be%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20determination%20to%20stand%20again%20that%20eases%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20path%20back%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20most%20experienced%20leaders%20are%20bad%20at%20making%20that%20brave%20decision%20to%20leave%20the%20political%20field%20of%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Ffrino%5C%22%3EAndrew%20Whitehead%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20honorary%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Nottingham%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20a%20former%20BBC%20India%20correspondent.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ELondon%20Calling%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0How%20does%20India%20look%20from%20afar%3F%20Looming%20world%20power%20or%20dysfunctional%20democracy%3F%20And%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20in%20Britain%2C%20and%20the%20West%2C%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20know%20about%20and%20perhaps%20learn%20from%3F%20This%20fortnightly%20column%20helps%20forge%20the%20connections%20so%20essential%20in%20our%20globalising%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705545049000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17160227%2F53067277451_4b2a5a1524_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ftrump-breaks-the-ice-in-iowa%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump%20seems%20set%20to%20be%20the%20Republican%20candidate%20for%20a%20third%20successive%20presidential%20election%2C%20while%20Biden%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20Democrat