l%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68002939.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Ayodhya%20Looms%2C%20Must%20Underline%20Yogi's%20Erosion%20of%20Goraknath's%20Syncretic%20Legacy%3A%20Lalu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17202547%2FLalu-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20president%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20in%20one%20of%20his%20first%20responses%20to%20the%20hype%20around%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20Ram%20Temple%20inauguration%20ceremony%20recalled%20how%20the%20syncretic%20tradition%20of%20the%20Gorakhnath%20temple%20was%20reversed%20when%20it%20fell%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20chiefs%20like%20the%20current%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Hindutva%20leader%20Adityanath.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYadav%20also%20spoke%20to%20reporters%20earlier%20on%20Wednesday%20(January%2017)%20to%20confirm%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fseat-sharing-ayodhya-lalu-prasad-9113703%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20will%20not%20be%20attending%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Ayodhya%20event.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20his%20biographer%20and%20senior%20journalist%20Nalin%20Verma%2C%20Yadav%20said%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Flalu-prasad-and-nalin-verma-write-a-new-beginning-in-ayodhya-and-end-of-an-inclusive-legacy-at-gorakhnath-9112374%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20an%20article%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20published%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cat%20a%20time%20when%20the%20lines%20between%20faith%20and%20politics%20are%20more%20blurred%20than%20ever%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20referring%20to%20the%20hyper-politicisation%20of%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20newly-built%20Ram%20temple%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20important%20to%20remember%20how%20Adityanath%20undermined%20the%20%E2%80%9Clegacy%20of%20inclusivity%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Gorakhnath%20Math%20to%20transform%20it%20into%20into%20a%20symbol%20of%20%E2%80%9Cexclusionary%20spirituality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20paradox%20that%20a%20leader%20who%20claims%20to%20be%20a%20follower%20of%20Gorakhnath%20practises%20a%20politics%20that%20undermines%20his%20legacy%20of%20inclusivity%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20article%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20goes%20on%20to%20narrate%20the%20syncretic%20practices%20of%20the%2011th-century%20Gorakhnath%20sect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20great%20Gorakhnath%20had%20his%20followers%20among%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20%E2%80%A6%20The%20credit%20for%20the%20present%20form%20of%20the%20%5BGorakhnath%5D%20temple%20%5Bin%20Gorakhpur%5D%2C%20spread%20over%2052%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20goes%20to%20Mahanta%20Buddhanath%20(1708-1723).%20Historical%20accounts%20suggest%20that%20Asaf-ud-Daulah%2C%20the%20nawab%20of%20Awadh%2C%20had%20donated%20the%20land%20to%20Baba%20Roshan%20Ali%2C%20a%20fakir%20and%20devotee%20of%20Gorakhnath%20in%20the%2018th%20century%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20helped%20rejuvenate%20the%20temple%20and%20added%20to%20its%20glory%20and%20grandeur.%20The%20tomb%20of%20Roshan%20Ali%2C%20opposite%20to%20the%20temple%2C%20constitutes%20the%20identity%20of%20Gorakhpur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYadav%20said%20that%20the%20politicisation%20of%20the%20Gorakhnath%20sect%20began%20in%201937%2C%20when%20Digvijaynath%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20assassination%20case%2C%20became%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emahant%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FqkSAOYTSgYo%3Fsi%3D7NuncwkelayseR2m%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDigvijaynath%20was%20also%20the%20first%20chief%20of%20the%20sect%20to%20enter%20electoral%20politics%20when%20he%20contested%20the%20Gorakhpur%20seat%20on%20a%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20ticket%20in%201967.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDigvijaynath%E2%80%99s%20successors%2C%20Avaidyanath%20and%20Adityanath%2C%20groomed%20themselves%20as%20symbols%20of%20militant%20Hindutva%20in%20the%20Gorakhpur%20region.%20Avaidyanath%20represented%20Gorakhpur%20in%20the%20Lucknow%20assembly%20%5Bseat%5D%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20several%20times.%20Adityanath%2C%20the%20present%20mahant%20and%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20also%20represented%20Gorakhpur%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20five%20times%20(1998-2014)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20article%20said%20that%20the%20politicisation%20of%20the%20temple%20undermined%20many%20love%20stories%2C%20like%20the%20legendary%20Heer%20Ranjha%20%5Bboth%20Muslims%5D%2C%20Sorthi-Brijbhar%2C%20and%20even%20bhajans%20of%20Kabir%2C%20Nanak%2C%20Raisad%2C%20Dadu%20and%20Meera.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Nath%20sect%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20accept%20the%20supremacy%20of%20Brahmins.%20The%20followers%20of%20the%20sect%20chose%20their%20gurus%20from%20their%20communities%20of%20weavers%2C%20dyers%2C%20shepherds%20and%20agriculturists.%20Gurus%20and%20disciples%20wander%20together%20for%20alms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%5BNoted%20Hindi%20writer%20Hazari%20Prasad%5D%20Dwivedi%20says%20that%20people%20from%20the%20lower%20strata%20of%20society%20in%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20who%20were%20looked%20down%20upon%20by%20the%20priestly%20class%20%E2%80%93%20became%20yogis%20%5Bof%20the%20Gorakhnath%20sect%5D%20in%20the%20north%20as%20well%20as%20to%20the%20south%20of%20the%20Vindhyas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EIn%20Photos%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fin-photos-heres-what-ayodhya-looks-like-now%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20What%20Ayodhya%20Looks%20Like%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYadav%20further%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20very%20passionate%20about%20these%20stories.%20When%20I%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%20in%201990%2C%20I%20got%20the%20folklorists%20to%20perform.%20I%20still%20get%20them%20to%20perform%20when%20I%20find%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20one%20of%20his%20recordings%2C%20the%20religious%20personality%20Osho%20recounts%20that%20once%2C%20the%20Hindi%20poet%20Sumitranandan%20Pant%20asked%20him%20to%20pick%2012%20major%20religious%20figures%20of%20India.%20Osho%20named%20Krishna%2C%20Patanjali%2C%20Gautam%20Buddha%2C%20Mahavir%2C%20Nagarjun%2C%20Shankar%2C%20Gorakhnath%2C%20Kabir%2C%20Nanak%2C%20Mira%20and%20Ram%20Krishna.%20Pant%20then%20asked%20him%20to%20cut%20down%20the%20list%20to%20seven%2C%20five%20and%20then%20four.%20Osho%20picked%20the%20names%20of%20Krishna%2C%20Patanjali%2C%20Buddha%20and%20Gorakhnath.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Pant%20asked%20him%20to%20further%20shorten%20the%20list%20to%20only%20three%2C%20Osho%20refused.%20Why%20could%20he%20not%20leave%20out%20Gorakhnath%2C%20Pant%20asked.%20I%20cannot%20leave%20him%2C%20Osho%20replied%2C%20because%20Gorakhnath%20opened%20a%20new%20avenue%20and%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20new%20religion.%20Without%20him%2C%20there%20would%20be%20no%20Kabir%20or%20Nanak.%20There%20would%20neither%20be%20Dadu%2C%20nor%20Wajid%2C%20Farid%20or%20Meera.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20Bhakti%20and%20Sufi%20tradition%20of%20India%20are%20indebted%20to%20Gorakhnath.%20Nobody%20equals%20him%20in%20his%20teachings%20that%20lead%20to%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20inner%20soul.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Yadav%20was%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20had%20stopped%20the%20Rath%20Yatra%20led%20by%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%20passing%20through%20Bihar%20on%20October%2023%2C%201990%2C%20and%20had%20the%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20arrested.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705504844000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17202547%2FLalu-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Flalu-yadav-ayodhya-gorakhnath%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20was%20especially%20important%20as%20this%20is%20a%20time%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20the%20lines%20between%20faith%20and%20politics%20are%20more%20blurred%20than%20ever%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20former%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20hyper-politicisation%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple's%20consecration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Flalu-yadav-ayodhya-gorakhnath%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HDFC%20Bank%20slide%20triggers%20worst%20day%20for%20market%20in%20last%2018%20months%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705504661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F03%2Ffull%2F1696329652-4074.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhdfc-bank-slide-triggers-worst-day-for-market-in-last-18-months-124011700846_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20decline%20in%20the%20markets%20wiped%20Rs%204.59%20trillion%20off%20investors'%20wealth.%20The%20India%20VIX%20--%20gauge%20of%20volatility%20--%20rose%20to%