3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20this%2C%20a%20part%20of%20the%20main%20structure%20of%20this%20mega%20project%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Falarm-bells-ring-over-kaleshwaram-project-after-a-few-pillars-of-medigadda-barrage-sink%2Farticleshow%2F104636872.cms%5C%22%3Eliterally%20sank%20into%20the%20Godavari%20River%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20night%20of%20October%2021.%20Forty%20days%20later%2C%20the%20BRS%20government%20itself%20sunk%20and%20lost%20the%20assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20new%20government%20has%20inherited%20this%20massive%20project%20in%20bad%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20article%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20provide%20a%20framework%20for%20the%20new%20government%20to%20address%20the%20KLIP%E2%80%99s%20issues%20and%20retrieve%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20larger%20interests%20of%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17173806%2FATM-1024x1024.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17173806%2FATM-1024x1024.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17173806%2FATM-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17173806%2FATM-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17173806%2FATM.jpeg%201152w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693376%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20KLIP%20became%20a%20major%20political%20issue%20ahead%20of%20the%202023%20Telangana%20assembly%20election.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40MirzaSiraj_INC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETelangana%20and%20the%20KLIP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20are%20not%20familiar%20with%20the%20KLIP%20and%20Telangana%2C%20this%20brief%20description%20might%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20prolonged%20agitation%2C%20Telangana%20was%20established%20in%202014%20by%20dividing%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Water%20was%20one%20of%20the%20three%20main%20reasons%20for%20this%20more%20than%20half-century-long%20agitation%20for%20separate%20statehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20region%2C%20which%20is%20mostly%20located%20in%20the%20Deccan%20plateau%20at%20higher%20elevations%2C%20was%20not%20getting%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20water%20allocated%20to%20the%20combined%20state%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20This%20is%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20region%20contains%20large%20parts%20of%20the%20Godavari%20and%20Krishna%20basins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Krishna%20River%2C%20which%20flows%20through%20the%20south%20of%20Telangana%2C%20does%20not%20have%20much%20water%20left%20due%20to%20various%20projects%20upstream%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20downstream%20in%20the%20coastal%20region.%20The%20Godavari%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20north%20of%20Telangana%2C%20does%20have%20plenty%20of%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20is%20needed%20in%20the%20uplands%20located%20higher%20than%20400%20metres%20above%20sea%20level%2C%20whereas%20the%20Godavari%20in%20Telangana%20has%20plenty%20of%20water%20along%20its%20course%20located%20less%20than%20100%20metres%20above%20sea%20level.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20only%20solution%20for%20getting%20water%20to%20the%20uplands%20is%20lift%20irrigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELift%20irrigation%20is%20inherently%20expensive.%20As%20mentioned%20above%2C%20water%20is%20a%20very%20emotional%20issue%20in%20Telangana%3B%20as%20a%20result%2C%20lift%20irrigation%20got%20wider%20political%20and%20public%20acceptance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20combined%20state%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20several%20lift%20irrigation%20projects%20were%20announced%20for%20the%20Telangana%20region%2C%20mostly%20to%20pacify%20the%20agitation%20for%20a%20separate%20state.%20One%20such%20attempt%20was%20made%20by%20the%20then-Congress%20government%20in%202007%20by%20initiating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Freshaping-pranahitha-chevella-into-kaleshwaram%2Farticle28089515.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20Pranahita-Chevella%20lift%20irrigation%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20later%20renamed%20as%20the%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20lift%20irrigation%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20basic%20concept%20of%20the%20project%20is%20to%20divert%20water%20from%20the%20Pranahita%2C%20which%20is%20a%20tributary%20of%20the%20Godavari%2C%20to%20Yellampalli%2C%20which%20is%20on%20the%20main%20Godavari%20River.%20From%20here%2C%20the%20water%20is%20lifted%20several%20times%20and%20transported%20through%20tunnels%20and%20canals%20to%20provide%20water%20for%20irrigation%20and%20drinking%20water%20to%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20is%20then%20transported%20further%20south%20till%20a%20town%20named%20Chevella%20(hence%20the%20name%20of%20the%20project).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20KLIP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%20and%20significantly%20modified%20the%20Pranahita-Chevella%20project%20in%202016%20and%20renamed%20it%20as%20the%20KLIP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaleshwaram%20is%20a%20small%20town%20on%20the%20right%20bank%20of%20the%20Godavari.%20This%20remote%20and%20sleepy%20pilgrimage%20place%20has%20now%20become%20a%20household%20name%20for%20this%20rather%20controversial%20lift%20irrigation%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20basic%20concept%20and%20strategy%20of%20the%20KLIP%20remained%20the%20same%20as%20that%20of%20the%20earlier%20project%2C%20which%20is%20to%20lift%20water%20to%20a%20height%20of%20about%20500%20metres%20from%20the%20Godavari%20and%20transport%20it%20400%20km%20to%20Medak%2C%20to%20Hyderabad%20city%20and%20further%20west%20into%20Rangareddy%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20government%20made%20three%20major%20changes%20to%20the%20project%20and%20increased%20its%20size%20and%20scope%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20very%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20was%20implemented%20through%20the%20engineering%2C%20procurement%20and%20construction%20(EPC)%20system%20of%20contracting%20introduced%20earlier.%20EPC%20contracting%20is%20opaque%2C%20and%20the%20resulting%20difficulty%20in%20tracking%20component%20and%20construction%20costs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fbjp-demands-cbi-probe-into-kaleshwaram-project%2Farticle67654324.ece%5C%22%3Emakes%20it%20easy%20for%20others%20to%20allege%20corruption%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20making%20these%20structural%20changes%2C%20the%20BRS%20projected%20this%20approach%20as%20far%20better%20and%20far%20more%20suitable%20than%20that%20of%20the%20earlier%20Pranahita-Chevella%20project.%20The%20KLIP%20was%20also%20marketed%20as%20the%20saviour%20of%20farming%20in%20Telangana%2C%20not%20only%20by%20the%20then-government%20but%20even%20by%20Union%20government%20agencies%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FHyderabad%2Fnabard-glad-to-be-part-of-telanganas-growth%2Farticle33917335.ece%5C%22%3ENABARD%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FHyderabad%2Fcwc-chairman-pats-ts-on-kaleshwaram-project%2Farticle23484935.ece%5C%22%3ECentral%20Water%20Commission%20(CWC)%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20are%20the%20three%20changes%20made%20by%20the%20BRS%20government%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Shifting%20the%20primary%20intake%20point%20from%20the%20Pranahita%20at%20Thummidihatti%20village%20(close%20to%20the%20Maharashtra%20border)%20to%20Medigadda%2C%20just%20downstream%20from%20Kaleshwaram%20on%20the%20main%20Godavari%20River%20after%20its%20confluence%20with%20the%20Pranahita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20change%20of%20intake%20points%20means%20using%20the%20main%20Godavari%20River%20as%20a%20storage%20reservoir%2C%20requiring%20the%20pumping%20of%20water%20upstream%20with%20three%20barrages%20and%20several%20dozens%20of%20high-capacity%2C%20high-speed%20pumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Increasing%20the%20pumping%20capacity%20to%20215%20tmc%2C%20which%20required%20large%20storage%20reservoirs.%20A%20consequence%20of%20this%20was%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20Mallannasagar%20Reservoir%2C%20which%20has%20a%20capacity%20of%2050%20tmc%2C%20is%20located%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere%20and%20required%20the%20uprooting%20of%2022%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Massive%20increase%20in%20cost%3A%20This%20increased%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20project%20from%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%20to%20almost%20Rs%201%2C27%2C872%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20reengineered%2C%20re-branded%20project%20had%20the%20following%20three%20stated%20objectives%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20New%20irrigation%20for%2019.63%20lakh%20acres%20and%20stabilisation%20for%20another%2018.82%20lakh%20acres%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Providing%20thirty%20tmc%20drinking%20water%20for%20Hyderabad%20and%20ten%20tmc%20for%20villages%20en%20route%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Providing%20sixteen%20tmc%20water%20for%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20three%20barrages%2C%2015%20storage%20facilities%2C%201531%20km%20of%20gravity%20canals%2C%20203%20km%20of%20tunnels%20and%2021%20pump%20houses%2C%20the%20project%20became%20massive%20and%20complex.%20The%20estimated%20power%20demand%20is%204%2C959%20MW%20and%2019%20sub-stations%20were%20to%20be%20built%20for%20this%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17174651%2FKLIP-2-1024x576.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17174651%2FKLIP-2-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17174651%2FKLIP-2-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17174651%2FKLIP-2.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693378%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20X%2F%40KTRBRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20a%20simple%20irrigation%20project%2C%20as%20was%20the%20case%20with%20most%20other%20irrigation%20projects.%20This%20level%20of%20complexity%20in%20construction%20and%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20these%20works%20were%20taken%20up%20have%20almost%20became%20a%20national%20spectacle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20purpose%20and%20cost%20of%20operating%20this%20system%20all%20became%20secondary.%20At%20one%20stage%2C%20the%20project%20became%20a%20must-visit%20destination%20for%20whoever%20visited%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20it%20started%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Ftelangana%2F2016%2Fnov%2F20%2Ftjac-to-release-report-on-lift-irrigation-projects-in-ts-1540655.html%5C%22%3Ecivil%20society%20critically%20analysed%20the%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20presented%20its%20findings%20to%20the%20Telangana%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F383918252%2FProject-Analysis-of-kaleshwaram%5C%22%3ETheir%20constructive%20advice%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-white-elephant-in-the-making%2Farticle24584314.ece%5C%22%3Elater%20critical%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20all%20were%20ignored.%20Any%20attempt%20to%20scrutinise%20the%20cost%20of%20water%20delivery%20was%20met%20with%20ridicule%20and%20even%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%98anti-Telangana%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98anti-national%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Ftelangana-kaleshwaram-kcr-conspiracy-theory%5C%22%3Ekey%20infrastructure%20was%20flooded%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20any%20criticism%20of%20the%20project%20even%20at%20this%20stage%20was%20largely%20ignored%20by%20both%20the%20state%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fbyline%2Fbiksham-gujja%5C%22%3EUnion%20governments%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20mention%20three%20key%20points%20which%20reflect%20the%20thinking%20of%20the%20political%20establishment%20in%20India%2C%20particularly%20related%20to%20agriculture%20and%20large%20water-infrastructure%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20these%20projects%20are%20presented%20as%20a%20national%20good%20based%20on%20these%20outdated%20and%20outlived%20concepts%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(a)%20Water%20is%20wasted%20when%20it%20goes%20to%20sea%2C%20so%20all%20river%20water%20must%20be%20used%20to%20the%20last%20drop%2C%20(b)%20more%20irrigation%20is%20good%20for%20the%20country%20and%20(c)%20irrigation%20must%20occur%20at%20any%20cost%2C%20including%20without%20any%20analysis%20of%20the%20operation%20and%20maintenance%20costs%20of%20lift%20irrigation%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20concepts%20were%20to%20some%20extent%20relevant%20then%20when%20India%20was%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20food%20security%20for%20its%20growing%20population.%20Also%2C%20most%20of%20those%20investments%20then%20were%20on%20gravity-based%20irrigation%20projects%20with%20little%20annual%20operation%20and%20maintenance%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20establishment%20has%20continued%20endorsing%20these%20concepts%20and%20invested%20in%20complex%20lift%20irrigation%20projects%2C%20which%20require%20huge%20capital%20costs%20as%20well%20as%20operation%20and%20maintenance%20costs%2C%20which%20exceed%20even%20the%20total%20value%20of%20crops%20cultivated%20by%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20this%2C%20most%20of%20these%20irrigation%20projects%20are%20being%20built%20by%20taking%20loans%20with%20commercial%20levels%C2%A0of%C2%A0interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20irrigation%20projects%20are%20not%20about%20farmers%20or%20food%20security%3B%20they%20are%20driven%20largely%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20keep%20construction%20contracts%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20mega%20projects%20are%20being%20built%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20clear%20guidelines%20on%20(a)%20the%20cost%20of%20water%20delivery%2C%20(b)%20limits%20on%20state%20governments%20to%20create%20special%20purpose%20vehicles%20(SPVs)%20for%20any%20unproductive%20projects%2C%20(c)%20technical%20and%20quality%20oversight%20of%20project%20designs%20and%20construction%2C%20and%20(d)%20restrictions%20on%20commercial%20banks%E2%80%99%20lending%20to%20such%20projects%2C%20which%20have%20no%20benefits%20to%20the%20country%2C%20all%20played%20a%20role%20in%20conceiving%20and%20constructing%20projects%20such%20as%20the%20KLIP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20prevailing%20situation%2C%20any%20state%20government%20can%20create%20an%20SPV%20and%20borrow%20money%20to%20construct%20any%20irrigation%20project%20with%20no%20economic%20logic%2C%20creating%20long-term%20economic%20consequences%20for%20future%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnless%20clear%20policy%20framework%20and%20guidelines%20are%20in%20place%2C%20projects%20such%20as%20the%20KLIP%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20constructed%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Ftelangana-kaleshwaram-kcr-conspiracy-theory%5C%22%3EWild%20Conspiracy%20Theories%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Fix%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20Very%20Real%20Problems%20in%20Kaleshwaram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20current%20situation%20of%20the%20KLIP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20So%20far%2C%20Rs%2093%2C782%20crore%20has%20been%20spent%20on%20the%20project%20since%202016.%20(The%20earlier%20amounts%20were%20not%20included.)%20Of%20this%2C%20the%20Telangana%20government%20spent%20Rs%2032%2C203%20crore%20and%20Rs%2061%2C665%20crore%20has%20been%20borrowed%20from%20commercial%20banks.%20Data%20also%20indicate%20that%20the%20state%20government%20has%20already%20started%20paying%20loans%20and%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20Telangana%20government%20has%20already%20spent%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%2022%2C700%20crore%20as%20part%20of%20its%20debt%20service.%20Of%20that%2C%20Rs%2017%2C700%20crore%20is%20towards%20interest.%20The%20major%20loan%20repayment%20started%20in%202023-24%20with%20annual%20instalments%20of%20Rs%2013%2C000%20crore.%20This%20will%20go%20on%20for%20the%20next%2013%20years%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20In%20addition%20to%20money%2C%20this%20project%20required%20close%20to%201%2C00%2C000%20acres%20of%20land%3B%20of%20that%2C%2066%2C000%20acres%20were%20acquired%20for%20infrastructure%20purposes%2C%20displacing%20many%20farmers%20and%20rural%20people.%20As%20mentioned%20above%2C%20Mallannasagar%20single-handedly%20displaced%20more%20than%2022%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20So%20far%2C%20just%2098%2C000%20acres%20of%20ayacut%20were%20created.%20This%20is%20just%205%25%20of%20the%20total%20(19.6%20lakh%20acres)%20expected%20to%20be%20created.%20No%20additional%20water%20for%20industry%20or%20drinking%20was%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20project%E2%80%99s%20key%20infrastructure%20is%20crumbling%20at%20an%20alarming%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20two%20of%20the%20three%20major%20pumping%20stations%20on%20the%20Godavari%20were%20submerged%20due%20to%20floods%2C%20and%20in%202023%2C%20the%20first%20intake%20point%20(from%20where%20all%20the%20water%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20pumped)%20experienced%20a%20major%20structural%20problem.%20The%20barrage%20across%20the%20main%20Godavari%20River%20started%20sinking.%20After%20that%2C%20two%20more%20barrages%20upstream%20are%20supposed%20to%20have%20developed%20similar%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20Mallannasagar%20reservoir%2C%20which%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20storing%2050%20tmc%20of%20water%2C%20is%20not%20being%20filled%20out%20of%20safety-related%20fears.%20The%20reservoir%20has%20been%20built%20on%20a%20geological%20fault%20line.%20After%20filling%20just%2015%20tmc%20(less%20than%20one-third%20of%20its%20capacity)%2C%20some%20leakages%20have%20been%20reported.%20If%20this%20structure%20fails%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20major%20catastrophe%20for%20the%20nearby%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Based%20on%20recently%20released%20data%20on%20electricity%20consumption%20for%20pumping%20water%20to%20various%20locations%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20electricity%20for%20providing%20water%20for%20irrigating%20each%20acre%20of%20land%20will%20be%20around%20Rs%2080%2C000%20to%20even%20Rs%201%2C00%2C000%20per%20season.%20This%20far%20exceeds%20the%20total%20value%20of%20the%20crop.%20This%20cost%20is%20not%20considering%20the%20capital%20cost%3B%20it%20is%20just%20the%20yearly%20cost%20of%20providing%20water%20to%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20single%20sentence%2C%20this%20mega%20project%20is%20in%20utter%20and%20total%20disarray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20will%20be%20a%20major%20burden%20on%20the%20new%20government%2C%20whose%20prospects%20will%20be%20negatively%20impacted%20if%20it%20does%20not%20understand%20the%20project%20and%20put%20together%20systems%20to%20deal%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20way%20forward%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20new%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20the%20KLIP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fministers-blame-previous-brs-govt-for-kaleshwaram-project-fiasco%2Farticle67686605.ece%5C%22%3Efigured%20prominently%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20press%20conferences%2C%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20expressed%20his%20intention%20to%20%E2%80%98expose%E2%80%99%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20irregularities%20and%20order%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fcm-sends-a-strong-signal-on-govts-intentions-on-kaleshwaram-project-lapses%2Farticle67648555.ece%5C%22%3Einvestigation%20headed%20by%20a%20sitting%20high%20court%20judge%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftelanganatoday.com%2Futtam-kumar-reddy-warns-legal-action-on-failure-to-repair-kaleshwaram-project%5C%22%3Enew%20irrigation%20minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20negotiating%20with%20the%20company%20that%20constructed%20the%20Medigadda%20barrage%20to%20repair%20the%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20new%20government%20makes%20any%20attempt%20to%20repair%20the%20KLIP%E2%80%99s%20crumbling%20infrastructure%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20have%20clarity%20on%20the%20following%20three%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Is%20the%20infrastructure%20safe%20and%20secure%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20How%20much%20it%20will%20cost%20annually%20to%20provide%20water%20for%20each%20acre%20of%20irrigation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20What%20institutional%20mechanism%20is%20needed%20to%20manage%20the%20project%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20effective%20and%20rational%20way%20of%20getting%20clarity%20on%20these%20questions%20is%20to%20commission%20a%20review%20of%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20suggest%20the%20following%20process%20in%20order%20to%20get%20a%20comprehensive%20view%20of%20the%20project.%20Until%20such%20a%20process%20is%20complete%2C%20the%20new%20government%20may%20have%20to%20avoid%20any%20new%20construction%20or%20repairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EReview%20of%20existing%20infrastructure%3A%20The%20state%20government%20may%20approach%20the%20National%20Dam%20Safety%20Authority%20to%20constitute%20a%20committee%20with%20experts%20from%20the%20CWC%20as%20well%20as%20international%20experts%20to%20review%20the%20safety%2C%20security%20and%20reliability%20of%20all%20the%20structures%20constructed%20as%20part%20of%20the%20KLIP.%20The%20Union%20government%20should%20be%20able%20to%20help%20the%20state%20government%20in%20this%20process%2C%20including%20by%20providing%20financial%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECost-benefit%20analysis%3A%20An%20independent%20international%20agency%2C%20such%20as%20the%20ADB%2C%20must%20be%20hired%20to%20review%20the%20operation%20and%20maintenance%20cost%20of%20the%20project%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20costs%20of%20electricity%20and%20other%20costs%20in%20delivering%20water%20to%20farmers%20at%20each%20elevation.%20Such%20a%20review%20will%20significantly%20help%20in%20taking%20policy%20decisions%20on%20which%20parts%20of%20the%20KLIP%20are%20most%20useful%20and%20which%20parts%20need%20re-orientation%20or%20a%20relook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Re-structuring%20loans%3A%20The%20Kaleshwaram%20Lift%20Irrigation%20Corporation%2C%20a%20state%20government%20SPV%20has%20been%20created%20to%20borrow%20loans%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20state%20government%2C%20which%20has%20guaranteed%20the%20loans%2C%20must%20pay%20them%20back.%20The%20annual%20payment%20from%202024%20is%20about%20Rs%2013%2C000%20crore%20a%20year.%20Several%20public%20sector%20banks%2C%20the%20Rural%20Electrification%20Corporation%20and%20NABARD%20have%20given%20loans%20without%20going%20through%20any%20technical%20and%20financial%20review.%20On%20top%20of%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20crumbling%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20SPV%20is%20almost%20bankrupt%20and%20has%20no%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20government%20should%20ask%20these%20banks%20to%20re-structure%20their%20loans%20and%20re-negotiate%20the%20interest.%20This%20is%20most%20important%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20undue%20burden%20on%20state%20finances.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fkaleshwaram-lift-irrigation-project-nirmala-sitharaman-shekhawat%5C%22%3EUnion%20finance%20minister%20has%20herself%20publicly%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Telangana%20government%20borrowed%20at%20high%20interest%20rates%20for%20this%20project%20and%20therefore%20the%20Union%20government%20might%20help%20in%20the%20process%20of%20restructuring%20the%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Institutional%20mechanism%3A%20A%20separate%20institutional%20mechanism%20to%20deal%20with%20this%20project%2C%20and%20the%20process%20of%20review%20and%20loan%20negotiations%2C%20must%20be%20established.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20KLIP%20is%20one%20of%20the%20costliest%20irrigation%20projects%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%20Even%20ignoring%20its%20massive%20capital%20cost%20and%20structural%20failures%2C%20the%20project%20requires%20at%20least%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20to%20Rs%2012%2C000%20crore%20for%20annual%20maintenance%20towards%20electricity%20and%20other%20costs.%20This%20project%20will%20also%20pose%20a%20major%20policy%20challenge%20to%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20government%20for%20several%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%E2%80%99s%20people%20are%20expecting%20rational%20decisions%20by%20this%20government.%20Based%20on%20reports%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20new%20government%20is%20contemplating%20certain%20options%2C%20which%20include%20(a)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelanganas-kaleshwaram-project-likely-to-be-defunct-for-at-least-seven-months-101704135865481.html%5C%22%3Eclosing%20the%20entire%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20(b)%20spending%20large%20sums%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Futtam-wants-designers-and-executing-agency-to-take-responsibility-for-medigadda-barrage-fiasco%2Farticle67651438.ece%5C%22%3Eto%20repair%20damaged%3C%2Fa%3E%20structures%20and%20(c)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Ftelangana%2Ftelangana-government-looks-to-revive-pranahita-chevella-project-as-it-paints-kaleshwaram-as-brs-blunder%2F%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20structures%20to%20bring%20water%20from%20other%20locations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20options%20should%20emerge%20from%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20process.%20Without%20such%20a%20process%2C%20any%20decision%20could%20certainly%20lead%20to%20even%20more%20financial%20and%20operational%20problems%20and%20pose%20even%20greater%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell-structured%20reviews%20with%20national%20and%20international%20experts%20on%20the%20safety%20and%20stability%20of%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20structures%2C%20and%20on%20its%20cost%20benefits%2C%20will%20surely%20come%20out%20as%20the%20best%20possible%20solution%20to%20this%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20massive%20public%20money%20amounting%20to%20more%20than%20Rs%201%2C20%2C000%20crore%20has%20been%20spent.%20Any%20additional%20money%20on%20this%20project%20should%20be%20based%20on%20the%20recommendations%20of%20a%20credible%20and%20independent%20review%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20people%20to%20take%20wise%20and%20informed%20decisions.%20Any%20hasty%20decision%20to%20close%20the%20entire%20project%20or%20to%20rush%20to%20alternative%20locations%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20further%20waste%20of%20money.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20only%20clear%20and%20wise%20option%20in%20front%20of%20this%20government%20is%20to%20commission%20these%20reviews%20at%20the%20earliest%20without%20any%20further%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%2