%20how%20it%20works%2C%20Murthy%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20I%20counsel%20the%20victim%20as%20most%20of%20the%20time%20they%20end%20up%20having%20suicidal%20thoughts.%20After%20listening%20to%20my%20journey%2C%20they%20feel%20motivated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20Murthy%20offers%20technical%20solutions.%20%E2%80%9CI%20check%20if%20their%20phone%20is%20hacked.%20I%20remove%20all%20the%20permissions%20from%20the%20fraudulent%20apps%20and%20protect%20data%20breaches.%20I%20advise%20them%20to%20change%20the%20phone%20number.%20In%20cases%20of%20harassment%20and%20defamation%2C%20I%20also%20help%20the%20victims%20find%20the%20locations%20of%20the%20criminals%20using%20IP%20addresses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurthy%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20has%20not%20only%20helped%20other%20victims%20but%20also%20helped%20him%20regain%20his%20identity%20and%20affection%20from%20his%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20only%20after%20a%20year%20when%20my%20father%20finally%20understood%20me.%20He%20literally%20took%20me%20into%20his%20arms%20and%20broke%20down%20for%20having%20misunderstood%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Murthy%20worked%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Commissioner%E2%80%99s%20cyber%20security%20volunteering%20force%20for%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-