our%20phone%20and%20contacts%20because%20Gmail%20is%20linked%20to%20your%20contacts%20and%20gallery.%20Also%2C%20you%20must%20mask%20the%20camera%20on%20your%20laptop%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Change%20your%20privacy%20settings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cases%20of%20cybercrime%2C%20firstly%20your%20WhatsApp%20is%20compromised.%20So%2C%20I%20suggest%20you%20ensure%20end-to-end%20encryption%20on%20WhatsApp.%20Also%2C%20many%20people%20do%20not%20know%20that%20they%20can%20choose%20%E2%80%98silence%20unknown%20callers%E2%80%99%20and%20protect%20their%20IP%20addresses%20by%20changing%20privacy%20settings.%20You%20must%20enable%20it%20to%20secure%20yourself%20from%20cybercriminals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Reboot%20your%20phone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179257%2Fmumbai-couple-troll-police-cyberbullying-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evictim%20of%20cybercrime%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20you%20should%20first%20deactivate%20your%20WhatsApp%20account%20immediately%20and%20remove%20photos%20from%20the%20gallery.%20Thereafter%2C%20you%20must%20reboot%20your%20phone.%20This%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20hacker%20loses%20access%20to%20your%20data%20and%20all%20the%20apps%20are%20closed%20automatically%2C%E2%80%9D%20suggests%20Murthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Reach%20out%20to%20the%20police%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20our%20work%2C%20we%20can%20trace%20the%20location%20but%20not%20the%20person.%20It%20is%20illegal.%20It%20is%20the%20police%20whom%20one%20should%20seek%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cases%20of%20harassment%20or%20defamation%20on%20social%20media%20verticals%20like%20Instagram%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20Facebook%2C%20police%20write%20to%20their